import React from 'react'
import ReactPDF , { PDFViewer,Document, Page, Text, View, StyleSheet } from '@react-pdf/renderer'
export default function PDFRender() {
  return (
    ReactPDF.render(
    <PDFViewer>
        <Document>
            <Page>
                <Text>welcome</Text>
            </Page>
        </Document>
    </PDFViewer>,'./helo.pdf')
  )
}
